import { Avatar, Box, Button, Stack, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import Theme from './Theme'
import img from '/media/nipuna/SSD FILES/Git Test/Medi-Ward-Sri-Lanka/src/Assest/mainlogo.png'

const theme=Theme();

export default function Sidebar() {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center">
        <Box marginTop="20px" marginBottom="20px"><Avatar sx={{
            width:100,
            height:100,
            backgroundColor:theme.palette.background.paper,
            }} alt="Remy Sharp" src={img} />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{width:"100%"}}>
            <Button sx={{
                width:"100%",
                height:70
            }}><Typography variant="h5">Home</Typography></Button>
        </Box>
        <Box>
            <Button size="large"><Typography variant="h5" sx={{color:theme.palette.background.normal}}>Scheduling</Typography></Button>
        </Box>
        <Box>
            <Button><Typography variant="h5">Leave Approve</Typography></Button>
        </Box>
        <Box>
            <Button><Typography variant="h5" >News</Typography></Button>
        </Box>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  )
}
